context:
The School of Fashion & Jewellery at George Brown College offers programs in fashion design and fashion business education. The school is ranked among the top 100 fashion schools in the world and is located in downtown Toronto, Canada's fashion capital. Programs provide industry-ready training through instructors with insider know-how, state-of-the-art equipment, and field education. Students have access to high-profile guest lecturers and networking events. The college covers the entire spectrum of fashion design and fashion business education from technology to the fundamentals of design, marketing, merchandising, manufacturing, and fashion management.
